nodes.text: The Jabiim Congress was the ruling body of the planet Jabiim. During the Clone Wars, it became influenced by Separatist sympathizers such as Alto Stratus, as well as their money, pushing Jabiim to join the Confederacy. Several months after the Clone Wars began, Stratus executed almost all of the Congressional Jabiimi Loyalists. Orliss Gillmunn was one of the few to escape.
